    "These images are crucial for the examination of colorectal conditions.",
    "We acquire and use colonoscopy images as datasets to advance contemporary diagnostic systems.",
    "We obtained images for the CKHK-22 dataset from three publicly accessible datasets.",
    "This study employed the CVC Clinic DB, Kvasir2, and Hyper Kvasir datasets.",
    "• The CVC Clinic DB 18: This dataset contained 1,640 images of polyps and nonpolyps, which were essential for the identification of polyps and the analysis of their formation."
